Initial police reports said that the victims Norma Magada , 44 ; and Robin Leuterio , 22 , jeepney driver , were in the area of Malasimbo Street , Barangay Masambong around 8:30 p.m. when one of the walls of L.G. Atkinson 's warehouse gave way .
Rescuers recovered Leuterio 's body in the rubble while Magada 's cadaver was found inside one of the buried jeepneys .
Reports said that the building was undergoing renovation when the accident happened .
Authorities are now looking into the possible filing of charges against the owner of the warehouse .
